HEADWORD: Mycteria
<hw>Mycteria</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A genus of birds including
certain of the wood ibises, including the endangered <spn>Mycteria
americana</spn>; it is sometimes assigned to a subfamily
<subfam>Mycteriinae</subfam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Mycteria</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
